OL,7,FA North East child poverty
OL,8,Forganisation has made renewed calls
OL,9,Ffor the Government to scrap the two-
OL,10,Fchild benefit cap after new figures
OL,11,Fshow a record number of children in
OL,12,Fthe region affected by the policy.
