OL,3,CNorth East Child Poverty Commission
OL,4,Crenews calls to scrap two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,FIt has now called on the new Labour
OL,8,FGovernment to scrap the policy adding
OL,9,Fthat it would be the most effective
OL,10,Fway for the Government to tackle child
OL,11,Fpoverty.
OL,13,FChair of the North East Child Poverty
OL,14,FCommission, Beth Farhat, said: "We
OL,15,Fhave warmly welcomed the new
OL,16,FGovernment's commitment to introduce
OL,17,Fan ambitious national child poverty
OL,18,Fstrategy.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
