OL,3,CNorth East Child Poverty Commission
OL,4,Crenews calls to scrap two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,F"This is desperately needed, and it
OL,8,Fmust recognise the importance of
OL,9,Finvesting more of our nation's wealth
OL,10,Fin children and families now, so that
OL,11,Fthey can access opportunities both
OL,12,Ftoday and in the future.
OL,14,F"It must also be evidence-led, and it
OL,15,Fis increasingly clear that there is no
OL,16,Froute to ending child poverty ` either
OL,17,Fin the North East or across the UK `
OL,18,Fthat does not involve scrapping the
OL,19,Ftwo-child limit.
