OL,3,CNorth East Child Poverty Commission
OL,4,Crenews calls to scrap two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,F"The new Government must make this an
OL,8,Fearly priority, if its child poverty
OL,9,Fplan is to be as meaningful as tens of
OL,10,Fthousands of kids growing up now in
OL,11,Fthe North East need it to be."
OL,13,FData released by the Department for
OL,14,FWork and Pensions on Thursday 11 July
OL,15,Fshows that as of April 2024 ` around
OL,16,F19,000 North East families were hit by
OL,17,Fthe two-child limit, of which just
OL,18,Fover 13,000 live in the North East
OL,19,FCombined Authority area and almost
OL,20,F6,000 live in Tees Valley.
