OL,3,CNorth East Child Poverty Commission
OL,4,Crenews calls to scrap two-child
OL,5,Cbenefit cap
OL,7,FIt also said there is an "extremely
OL,8,Fhigh" correlation between
OL,9,Fconstituencies with the highest child
OL,10,Fpoverty rates and those with the
OL,11,Fhighest proportions of children
OL,12,Faffected by the two-child limit.
OL,14,FIn the North East, 89% of all
OL,15,Fconstituencies have at least one in
OL,16,Ffour children growing up in poverty.
OL,18,FWork and Pensions Secretary of State
OL,19,FLiz Kendall MP: "Too many children are
OL,20,Fgrowing up in poverty and this is a
OL,21,Fstain on our society.
